high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink
Pick up the bar of soap that is sitting on the sink
Take a step back and continue to face the sink
Place the soap into the sink and turn on the water to rinse the soap, then turn off the water and pick up the soap
Take a step back and continue to face the sink but focus your attention to the trash can below the sink to the left
Place the bar of soap into the trash can above the yellow spray bottle
anns.task_desc: Place a bar of soap into a trash can

high_descs: Grab the pink bar of soap from the sink.
Walk to the edge of the sink.
Put the soap under the faucet, soak it, then grab it.
Locate the trash can under the sink.
Throw the soap bar away in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the trash can.

high_descs: Take a few steps to the right, to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap from the back of the sink.
Hold the soap and move slightly left to still face the sink.
Place the soap in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the soap.
Carry the soap and face to the left.
Place the soap in the trash can below.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and throw it away.
